            <div class="news-linknav"><a style="color:black" href="/More/Index?type=1011">公告通知</a><em>></em><a style="color:black" href="#">关于选拔优秀学生前往香港岭南大学攻读研究生的通知</a></div>
            <div class="news-mainContent">
                    <h2 style="border-bottom:none">关于选拔优秀学生前往香港岭南大学攻读研究生的通知</h2>
                    <h2 style="font-size:20px;">   </h2>
                    <br />
                <div class="markFrom">
                    来源： &nbsp&nbsp&nbsp点击次数：1300 次 &nbsp&nbsp&nbsp发布时间：2017-11-24 &nbsp&nbsp&nbsp作者：
                </div>
                <p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 24px;">关于选拔优秀学生前往香港岭南大学攻读研究生的通知</span></strong></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">各学部：</span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">为开拓学生国际视野，提供多方位的留学渠道，我校拟与香港岭南大学合作，开展研究生项目及其他项目。现该校</span><span style="font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">2018-2019</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">学年度研究生已经开始招生，具体情况如下：</span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">一、申请项目：</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent: 37px;"><span style="font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">1</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">、会计学硕士</span><span style="font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Master of Accountancy</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px;"><span style="font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">2</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">、金融学硕士</span><span style="font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Master of Science in Finance Programme</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px;"><span style="font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">3</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">、电商及供应链管理硕士</span><span style="font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Master of Science in eBusiness and Supply Chain Management</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px;"><span style="font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">4</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">、人力资源管理及组织行为学管理硕士</span><span style="font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">Master of Science in Human Resource Management &amp; OrganisationalBehaviourProgramme</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px;"><span style="font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">5</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">、市场营销及国际商务硕士</span><span style="font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;"> Master of Science in Marketing &amp; International Business</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">二、招收对象</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent: 37px;"><span style="font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">1</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">、经管学部</span><span style="font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">2014</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">级本科及往届毕业生。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px;"><span style="font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">2</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">、非经管学部学生需要在岭南大学学习预备课程。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">三、项目优势</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent: 37px;"><span style="font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">1</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">、拥有先进教育理念的世界级高等学府。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">岭南大学现为香港八大公立大学之一，世界博雅院校联盟成员，国际高等商学院协会（</span><a href="http://baike.baidu.com/view/545434.htm" target="http://baike.baidu.com/_blank"><span style="color: windowtext; font-size: 19px; text-underline: none;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">AACSB</span></span></a><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">）认证成员。</span><span style="font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">2015</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">年被《福布斯》评为亚洲十大顶尖博雅学院之一。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px;"><span style="font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">2</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">、较短的学习时间。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">授课式研究生学制一年。学制短，效率高，费用相对降低，学生可以更早投身工作或者进一步深造。</span></p><p style="background: white; text-align: justify; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 37px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">3</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">、纯正的英文教学。</span></p><p style="background: white; text-align: justify; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 37px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">无需远赴欧美，也可以在英文语境中学到纯正的英语，并且相对于英美国家，华人的面孔更能给留学生们带来亲切感。</span></p><p style="background: white; text-align: justify; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 37px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">4</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">、较低的留学门槛。</span></p><p style="background: white; text-align: justify; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 37px; -ms-text-justify: inter-ideograph;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">相对于拥有同样教育环境的英美国家，国内高校本科毕业生无需雅思托福成绩同样可以申请香港研究生。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">四、申请要求</span></strong></p><p style="text-indent: 37px;"><span style="font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">1</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">、本科学位证书和学历证书（</span><span style="font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">2014</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">级学生可以先提供在读证明）。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 37px;"><span style="font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">2</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">、英语六级不低于</span><span style="font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">450</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">分</span><span style="font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">/</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">雅思不低于</span><span style="font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">6.5/</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">托福不低于</span><span style="font-size: 19px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">79</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">。</span></p><ol class=" list-paddingleft-2" style="list-style-type: decimal;"><li><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">报名时间及地点</span></strong></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">请有意愿报名的同学于</span><span style="font-size: 19px;">2017</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">年</span><span style="font-size: 19px;">12</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">月</span><span style="font-size: 19px;">10</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">日前往文华学院国际交流处（行政楼</span><span style="font-size: 19px;">B223</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">）咨询报名。</span></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">咨询电话：</span><span style="font-size: 19px;">87582749</span></p></li><li><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">招生简章及申请表见附件</span></strong></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:;"><span style="font-size: 19px;">&nbsp;&nbsp; <strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:;"><span style="font-size: 19px;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align: right; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">国际交流处</span></p><p style="text-align: right; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:;"><span style="font-size: 19px;">2017</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">年</span><span style="font-size: 19px;">11</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">月</span><span style="font-size: 19px;">24</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 19px;">日</span></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:;"><span style="font-size: 19px;">&nbsp;</span></p></li></ol><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:;"><span style="font-size: 19px;"><br/></span></p><p style="line-height: 16px;"><img style="margin-right: 2px; vertical-align: middle;" src="http://www.hustwenhua.net/ueditor/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_rar.gif"/><a title="ApplicationForm201819.zip" style="color: rgb(0, 102, 204); font-size: 12px;" href="/ueditor/net/upload/file/20171124/6364713493908695341524102.zip">ApplicationForm201819.zip</a></p><p style="line-height: 16px;"><img style="margin-right: 2px; vertical-align: middle;" src="http://www.hustwenhua.net/ueditor/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_rar.gif"/><a title="RecommendationForm201819.zip" style="color: rgb(0, 102, 204); font-size: 12px;" href="/ueditor/net/upload/file/20171124/6364713493921296063497451.zip">RecommendationForm201819.zip</a></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family:;"><span style="font-size: 19px;"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p>
